46:58.990 --> 47:01.601
contains
highly sensitive material

47:01.731 --> 47:03.603
that could be very damaging
to the president

47:03.733 --> 47:05.083
if it were to get out.

47:07.520 --> 47:09.957
And...

47:10.088 --> 47:12.612
I have been instructed
to get rid of it.

47:18.357 --> 47:19.227
