and-and-and the other one--

47:52.478 --> 47:55.785
and, you know, I-I just can't
run the risk of this

47:55.916 --> 47:57.613
blowing back on Dick, you know.

47:57.744 --> 47:59.485
And that's why when I--when I
raised these very concerns

47:59.615 --> 48:03.141
to him personally yesterday,

48:03.271 --> 48:07.580
