48:49.491 --> 48:51.102
mad at me?

48:51.232 --> 48:53.278
Did I cross him in some way?

48:53.408 --> 48:56.542
Oh, no. No, no, no, no.
Gosh, no, no, no. No.

48:56.672 --> 48:57.717
You're looking at this
all wrong, Pat.

48:57.847 --> 48:59.023
